1
00:00:47,450 --> 00:00:51,920
♪ If I could escape from fate's predetermined path ♪

2
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:56,990
♪ And touch the true essence of time and space, the ultimate secret ♪

3
00:00:57,320 --> 00:01:02,190
♪ I'll awaken this extraordinary destiny ♪

4
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:04,879
♪ And awaken another version of myself ♪

5
00:01:05,850 --> 00:01:10,810
♪ The clearest, most resilient eyes of yours ♪

6
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:14,740
♪ Crystals filled with infinite power ♪

7
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,550
♪ Unleash my true nature ♪

8
00:01:17,570 --> 00:01:20,630
♪ Take every breath at lightning speed ♪

9
00:01:20,660 --> 00:01:22,600
♪ Shining justice ♪

10
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:27,120
♪ The only truth in the duel ♪

11
00:01:27,380 --> 00:01:29,720
♪ Now you guys are hearing my cry ♪

12
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:32,240
♪ My life was full of regrets ♪

13
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,979
♪ Restart ♪

14
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,300
♪ Striving, fighting, honing ♪

15
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,259
♪ Finding the future ♪

16
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:39,620
♪ Do not just dream it, have a try ♪

17
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:42,220
♪ Nothing can beat me, bravery's in my chest ♪

18
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:46,740
♪ I'll smash myself to protect your tenderness ♪

19
00:01:46,860 --> 00:01:50,800
♪ Never bow down again ♪

20
00:01:52,990 --> 00:01:57,240
[Super Cube]
[Episode 7]

21
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:16,840
Cube.

22
00:02:17,710 --> 00:02:19,440
You detected seven opponents.

23
00:02:21,110 --> 00:02:24,290
Logically, there should be two left upstairs.

24
00:02:29,940 --> 00:02:30,300
Yes.

25
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:34,290
But just now, one of them suddenly disappeared.

26
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,370
Disappeared?

27
00:02:37,940 --> 00:02:39,710
So... only one left?

28
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:46,540
As you said,

29
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,430
I'm your only opponent left.

30
00:02:50,650 --> 00:02:51,940
And me, Shan!

31
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:56,640
Master, their combat power is 7.

32
00:02:56,820 --> 00:02:59,030
Huh? Just a power of 7?

33
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:02,840
- It's an honor to meet you.
- It's an honor to meet you.

34
00:03:03,670 --> 00:03:04,720
- We are
- We are

35
00:03:05,890 --> 00:03:07,350
- Chu Mushan.
- Chu Mushan.

36
00:03:11,670 --> 00:03:13,690
Cube, sure you're not mistaken?

37
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,480
His combat power is just 7?

38
00:03:16,010 --> 00:03:16,430
Yes.

39
00:03:17,170 --> 00:03:19,970
But the interior of that puppet is very intricate,

40
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,579
with an intermediate gem inside.

41
00:03:23,660 --> 00:03:24,660
Don't be nervous.

42
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:27,670
You were on par with a Level-B warrior.

43
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,760
I'm afraid my head is as fragile as an egg to you.

44
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:32,760
However...

45
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:36,410
The Way of Nature: Excess is reduced

46
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,890
and deficiency supplemented!

47
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:48,079
Oh my god, what the hell was that?

48
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:51,990
Actually, aren't we destined to be archenemies?

49
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:56,339
You're a daredevil who relies solely on brute strength.

50
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:57,310
And I

51
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,930
rely on techniques.

52
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:03,080
Talismans, teleportation, puppetry—pure techniques!

53
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:10,110
I'm curious to know what will win: your strength

54
00:04:10,380 --> 00:04:12,240
or my sophisticated techniques?

55
00:04:53,990 --> 00:04:56,300
You're really growing on me.

56
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:35,880
{\an8}[Eye drops]

57
00:07:09,730 --> 00:07:14,960
Ou-Ou-Ouch! Let go! Stop! It really hurts!

58
00:07:15,090 --> 00:07:15,920
Let go!

59
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,130
Let go!

60
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:52,580
If he's an ordinary human,

61
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:54,700
then my full-force punch...

62
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:35,590
I can't believe I made the enemy worry about me.

63
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,620
Oops, how awkward.

64
00:08:39,690 --> 00:08:42,020
What the heck? How are you still standing?

65
00:08:42,179 --> 00:08:46,440
To think my Defensive Talisman would be exhausted by just one punch of yours.

66
00:08:46,850 --> 00:08:48,680
You sure are strong.

67
00:08:49,460 --> 00:08:52,210
If I don't get anything out of this fight with you,

68
00:08:53,140 --> 00:08:55,770
I'd have spent all that money for nothing!

69
00:09:02,450 --> 00:09:05,060
Temple of evil ghosts!

70
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:15,040
Anyone who sees this...

71
00:09:16,370 --> 00:09:18,070
must die!

72
00:09:18,210 --> 00:09:19,480
Shrink the distance!

73
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,559
Shrink! Shrink! Shrink!

74
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,520
So fast?

75
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:51,660
Dang it!

76
00:10:02,250 --> 00:10:03,920
Having fun, aren't you?

77
00:10:36,210 --> 00:10:39,820
The talisman stuck on your body... Any idea how much it costs?

78
00:10:40,190 --> 00:10:41,040
Who the...

79
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,470
hell cares?

80
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:43,980
For one,

81
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,180
700 grand!

82
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,860
So heavy!

83
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:50,330
This is the weight of 3.5 million!

84
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,510
Not bad.

85
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:13,630
Job well done.

86
00:11:23,460 --> 00:11:25,590
It's over already?

87
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:30,710
Warfare's really a money-burning game.

88
00:11:48,430 --> 00:11:51,490
What? Where'd you get the damn shovel?

89
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:53,680
How did he block it?

90
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:57,600
Surprised, huh?

91
00:11:58,510 --> 00:12:02,640
This is the strength of a locally-made farming shovel that costs a dollar!

92
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,690
Fine, let's play.

93
00:12:05,260 --> 00:12:07,160
I'm gonna add 140 million

94
00:12:07,230 --> 00:12:08,730
to kill you!

95
00:12:11,230 --> 00:12:13,119
This is how we, the Ominous Menaces,

96
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:16,580
are different from those barbarians of the Million Alliance!

97
00:12:17,930 --> 00:12:19,010
I get it now.

98
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:22,470
Did my punch give you a concussion?

99
00:12:36,390 --> 00:12:37,070
What?

100
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:40,200
He can't even mobilize his internal power.

101
00:12:40,420 --> 00:12:43,880
How does he know how to use the distance-shrinkage technique?

102
00:12:46,210 --> 00:12:47,940
Forcing me to use my trump card!

103
00:12:50,850 --> 00:12:51,850
You really are

104
00:12:52,300 --> 00:12:53,500
quite a piece of work.

105
00:13:00,010 --> 00:13:00,890
On you,

106
00:13:01,110 --> 00:13:03,310
there are still five Weight Talismans.

107
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,490
Let's see how long you can hold on.

108
00:13:08,770 --> 00:13:09,830
Why won't he budge?

109
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:13,920
Have you forgotten I'm now worth 3.5 million?

110
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:18,560
As they say, you reap what you sow!

111
00:14:38,690 --> 00:14:41,060
Young Master. We should go.

112
00:14:42,110 --> 00:14:43,110
I can't leave yet.

113
00:14:44,770 --> 00:14:46,950
Uncle, I know.

114
00:14:47,950 --> 00:14:49,210
You protect me because

115
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:52,810
if I, the third son of the Yans, suffer a tragic death,

116
00:14:53,180 --> 00:14:55,980
it'll bring shame on the prestigious family name.

117
00:14:56,270 --> 00:14:57,520
My duty

118
00:14:58,060 --> 00:15:00,260
is to ensure your safety, Young Master.

119
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:02,700
Uncle.

120
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,530
Don't forget

121
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:08,210
I still have a trump card to turn the tables.

122
00:15:09,190 --> 00:15:11,580
This is not some reckless revenge.

123
00:15:13,310 --> 00:15:15,290
I risked everything I had

124
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:17,770
to seize this opportunity.

125
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:20,570
In that case,

126
00:15:21,230 --> 00:15:22,800
I'll do my very best

127
00:15:23,490 --> 00:15:25,220
to ensure your safety.

128
00:15:32,060 --> 00:15:33,010
Goodbye.

129
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,010
No.

130
00:15:36,210 --> 00:15:37,540
It's farewell.

131
00:15:39,020 --> 00:15:41,480
Although my execution hasn't been perfect,

132
00:15:41,770 --> 00:15:43,990
everything's still under my control.

133
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:47,160
Wang Xiaoxiu.

134
00:15:47,550 --> 00:15:48,900
Go to hell!

135
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:03,800
Break!

136
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:07,810
Break! Break!

137
00:16:09,470 --> 00:16:10,630
What's going on?

138
00:16:10,740 --> 00:16:12,150
Screw you, bastard!

139
00:16:13,900 --> 00:16:14,590
What?

140
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:18,270
You're beyond crazy, you fool!

141
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:29,630
Yao...

142
00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:26,330
Yao...

143
00:18:27,410 --> 00:18:28,760
Yao...

144
00:18:29,530 --> 00:18:30,550
Yao!

145
00:18:36,300 --> 00:18:37,330
Where is she?

146
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:38,810
Master.

147
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:42,150
The enemy's energy dissipated almost instantly.

148
00:18:45,290 --> 00:18:46,200
Not bad.

149
00:18:47,370 --> 00:18:48,430
You fled real fast.

150
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:51,750
Yao.

151
00:18:52,350 --> 00:18:53,750
I'm coming to save you...

152
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:56,830
Wait for me!

153
00:19:06,490 --> 00:19:07,970
Is everyone gone?

154
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:11,950
Shen Yao! Are you there?

155
00:19:15,030 --> 00:19:15,780
You are...

156
00:19:17,230 --> 00:19:18,190
Huo Huan!

157
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,200
Where's Shen Yao?

158
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:24,640
Don't kill me! Please! Don't kill me!

159
00:19:25,290 --> 00:19:26,770
Tell me where Shen Yao is!

160
00:19:28,730 --> 00:19:30,530
Speak! Where is she?

161
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:43,370
Yao! Yao! Yao!

162
00:19:43,800 --> 00:19:44,930
I'm here to save you!

163
00:19:46,040 --> 00:19:48,640
Yao, don't be scared. It's fine now.

164
00:19:55,810 --> 00:19:58,179
Run, Xiaoxiu! There's a bomb on this chair.

165
00:19:58,180 --> 00:19:59,780
Once I get up, it'll explode!

166
00:20:06,150 --> 00:20:07,820
Xiaoxiu, save yourself.

167
00:20:07,950 --> 00:20:09,130
You must go now.

168
00:20:09,390 --> 00:20:10,120
Don't worry.

169
00:20:10,390 --> 00:20:11,800
This is nowhere near

170
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:14,110
the biggest bomb I've met today!

171
00:20:17,740 --> 00:20:20,400
This room's specially modified by Chu Mushan.

172
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:22,860
Master, you can't teleport in here.

173
00:20:23,860 --> 00:20:24,920
I'm gonna stay here

174
00:20:25,320 --> 00:20:27,520
and watch you two get blown up into mush!

175
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:28,380
Xiaoxiu!

176
00:20:28,630 --> 00:20:29,370
Cube.

177
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:31,630
How can I defuse the bomb safely?

178
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:35,340
Master, cut the wires in order of yellow, blue, green, and red.

179
00:20:41,700 --> 00:20:43,900
It'll just have to detonate in the cube.

180
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,400
Xiaoxiu!

181
00:20:51,060 --> 00:20:51,940
I'm here, Yao.

182
00:20:55,930 --> 00:20:56,860
You're safe now.

183
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:03,000
I won't... ever let...

184
00:21:17,780 --> 00:21:18,730
Xiaoxiu!

185
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:20,350
Why?

186
00:21:20,570 --> 00:21:21,830
Why didn't it explode?

187
00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:23,400
Xiaoxiu!

188
00:21:24,570 --> 00:21:26,630
Nothing will wreck my plan this time!

189
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:31,760
What's going on?

190
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:34,060
Damn it! I can't move!

191
00:21:34,810 --> 00:21:38,640
I didn't expect it to blow up the intermediate gem in the puppet!

192
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,470
Young Master.

193
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:41,939
The dangerous one is here.

194
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:43,040
We need to leave.

195
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,150
Yao...

196
00:21:50,910 --> 00:21:53,610
What on earth is going on?

197
00:21:56,900 --> 00:21:58,170
My... Yao...

198
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:06,270
Yao!

199
00:22:06,650 --> 00:22:08,170
Hang in there.

200
00:22:08,410 --> 00:22:09,590
I'll get you...

201
00:22:10,090 --> 00:22:12,200
to the hospital now...

202
00:22:12,970 --> 00:22:14,330
You can't save her.

203
00:22:17,740 --> 00:22:18,360
No!

204
00:22:20,890 --> 00:22:22,040
We made a pact.

205
00:22:22,430 --> 00:22:25,680
I'll protect her forever.

206
00:22:34,250 --> 00:22:35,870
You can't even save yourself.

207
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:39,280
{\an8}[Caution: Please do not try this at home]

208
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:46,780
Bastard! Give Yao back to me!

209
00:22:50,110 --> 00:22:51,190
Yao!

210
00:22:52,150 --> 00:22:53,110
You know nothing

211
00:22:54,140 --> 00:22:56,140
about her and the superhuman world.

212
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,530
I was the cause of this.

213
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:00,920
I'll take care of it.

214
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:07,000
Yao.

215
00:23:11,300 --> 00:23:13,180
Yao!

216
00:23:57,810 --> 00:24:00,640
I can't... get Yao back.

217
00:23:57,840 --> 00:24:02,110
{\an8}[Next Episode Preview]

218
00:24:00,760 --> 00:24:02,860
Wang Xiaoxiu, let's have a chat.

219
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:05,460
Boss, he's at least a Level B.

220
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:07,420
It's beyond our control.

221
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:09,040
What's your motive?

222
00:24:09,620 --> 00:24:10,450
Kiddo.

223
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:12,459
I've been looking all over for you.

224
00:24:12,460 --> 00:24:14,040
Why don't we compete?

225
00:24:14,300 --> 00:24:15,220
Compete?

226
00:24:15,470 --> 00:24:17,370
Help us complete three missions,

227
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,720
and you’ll know where Yan Luo is.

228
00:24:20,180 --> 00:24:20,840
One for one.

229
00:24:21,260 --> 00:24:21,990
One mission.

230
00:24:22,340 --> 00:24:23,270
Besides Yan Luo,

231
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:26,219
I'm even more interested in info on Xigu Qin.

232
00:24:26,220 --> 00:24:26,820
Deal.

233
00:24:28,630 --> 00:24:29,670
Please make your choice.

